page.title: 05LITTLE PARK NURSERY
page.content: The owner enjoyed his job.He said he has one thousand to six thousand customers per week,but it varies throughout the year.The hardest job is weeding.The nursery was commenced in 1965. They sell trees(ornamental),fruit trees, shrubs,roses,conifers,seeds and all gardening equipment.Each day they have to do watering, checking plants and,of course,serving the customers. There are five people employed there. This nursery has the widest selection of conifers in Suffolk,240 different kinds. THE DUKE OF MALBOROUGH PUB,SOMERSHAM. The Duke of Malbrough pub has been open since the fourteenth century. Every Tuesday there is a delivery of beer, crisps,peanuts and cigarettes. They open a 8.3Oam and close at 11.OOpm.
